{"tid":980031,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Final year 最後一個sem，頹到乜都冇做過點算","createTime":"2019-01-13T08:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T09:48:02.000Z","uid":167689,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d9c68b3afe8da97fae809e67497f1d4eb4f2cdd3","tid":980031,"uid":167689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"就開sem<br />\nFYP 冇做過<br />\n冇prep過grad job<br />\nsem break日日睇劇打機<br />\n有時瞓前思考人生自責下 瞓醒又係咁<br />\n求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b6f1116bd3af969b7ee25eb77c7e7bd61cb5b0","tid":980031,"uid":4985,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T08:03:08.000Z","msg":"same 再頹d係好大機要defer"},{"pid":"af1ff4e6fe10e602c7de8c752ea931ced366341e","tid":980031,"uid":58086,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T08:05:20.000Z","msg":"唔會有問題嘅<br />\n<br />\n你會完成到FYP<br />\nGrad完你最終都會搵到工<br />\n每日放左工你都會打機訓覺<br />\n<br />\n自責黎係無意義的，你遲早會明"},{"pid":"93fff4d5f13eca80bc4df33785f69f27c6a44374","tid":980031,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T08:05:31.000Z","msg":"defer lo"},{"pid":"fb9f905e2bed4d2f40206cad84b5c00b05ff79b2","tid":980031,"uid":167689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06b6f1116bd3af969b7ee25eb77c7e7bd61cb5b0","tid":980031,"uid":4985,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T08:03:08.000Z","msg":"same 再頹d係好大機要defer"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"以前有deadline有考試都會知驚<br />\n讀咗幾年 愈來愈麻木<br />\n踢一下郁一郁 依加冇人踢直頭唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82c8cf05085f51a1ed62d04ef197319621d2d01","tid":980031,"uid":222782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T08:50:45.000Z","msg":"再讀多個學位"},{"pid":"1908ab6ba31c4188bf58d32f312277f4340f4198","tid":980031,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"咩科"},{"pid":"3f3d0562b0f770dbf244c034033df6ad2f2435f7","tid":980031,"uid":159284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"開唔開sem都唔會做，都係頹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab75922b791382d2c20a13e9f12d8a806cb0e185","tid":980031,"uid":190658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"放心無事嫁<br />\n之後你嗰一個sem會hea住咁過,喺緊密嘅課堂同畢業嘅壓迫亂踢下成功pass晒啲subject。<br />\n唯獨要自己控制嘅FYP毫無進展,一直到sem尾嘅時候發現已經無法挽回。<br />\n只有兩種選擇:Fail同withdrawal subject 去避transcript有F出現<br />\n<br />\n從此,你嘅生活變得更悠閒,有更多時間睇劇打機.因為你需要等department再開科FYP俾你reg。中間段時間你或者會搵份工去應付屋企人同自己洗費.<br />\n<br />\n新學年sem1,你開一份新project或者department俾你可以做返同一份project,但點都好因為興趣唔大而一直拖直到sem尾。Loop或者交垃圾成為你嘅選擇。<br />\n選擇Loop嘅你會Loop到最長修讀年期然後進入交垃圾路線<br />\n選擇交垃圾嘅你會懷着不安與自責去買張主題公園年票用歡樂麻醉自己,視乎department決定而進入Loop路線,畢業或失業<br />\n<br />\n利申:行到交垃圾路線,買咗老鼠樂園年票"}]}